        <abstract>
            These specimens are extracted from online database of plant herbaria in China, with more than 60 herbaria. All the data are collected in other countries, not  inside China. So, it&amp;#39;s a very valuable resource to make a discovery to see the what specimens are stored in China, and more things could be done with these data.
        </abstract>
